250
00:15:53,077 --> 00:15:55,514
Ed,I'm gonna run tactics.

251
00:15:55,543 --> 00:15:57,923
You and Lou run Command Post.

252
00:15:58,892 --> 00:16:00,860
Wha... Command Post?

253
00:16:00,869 --> 00:16:02,961
Oprah says.

254
00:16:03,643 --> 00:16:05,907
