260
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:28,910
Get out of my way. My wife's
in there. Let me through.

261
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:30,762
Sarah! Let go of me!

262
00:16:30,772 --> 00:16:34,582
Joshua Scott. Mr. Scott.

263
00:16:35,541 --> 00:16:37,077
Thank you,Constable.

264
00:16:37,096 --> 00:16:38,027
What are you doing?

265
00:16:38,046 --> 00:16:39,351
We can't let you come any closer.

266
00:16:39,380 --> 00:16:41,606
