a fight,an argument.

283
00:17:16,644 --> 00:17:18,879
Your wife isn there with an
unknown weapon and a hostage,

284
00:17:18,927 --> 00:17:21,211
and we don't want to
make her more upset,okay?

285
00:17:21,231 --> 00:17:24,042
