291
00:17:42,813 --> 00:17:44,704
Unidentified hostage.

292
00:17:44,723 --> 00:17:47,487
Sergeant Parker to direct tactical plan.

293
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:51,402
How you doing? I'm Ed Lane. Louis Young.

294
00:17:51,690 --> 00:17:54,358
Have a seat, please,Josh.

295
00:17:55,701 --> 00:17:58,024
You texted him twice this morning.

296
00:17:58,033 --> 00:18:00,058
It's professional. I told you.

297
00:18:00,068 --> 00:18:02,352
